@startuml
title Fast Slow Escalation

actor User
participant "Fast Runtime" as Fast
participant "Retrieval Planner" as Planner
participant "Escalation Planner" as Escalate
participant "Slow Path" as Slow
database DB

User -> Fast: Ask question
Fast -> Planner: plan_retrieval(request)
Planner --> Fast: mode + budget

Fast -> DB: load bounded retrieval pack
DB --> Fast: profile / claims / notes /\ntasks / evidence

Fast -> Fast: draft answer
Fast -> Escalate: evaluate_conflict_uncertainty\n(draft, retrieval pack)

alt stay on fast path
    Escalate --> Fast: no escalation
    Fast --> User: answer
else escalate to slow path
    Escalate --> Fast: typed handoff required
    Fast -> Slow: typed handoff\n(user_goal, facts_we_believe,\nopen_questions, uncertainty_flags,\nrequired_outputs)
    Slow -> DB: fetch extra evidence if needed
    DB --> Slow: expanded retrieval pack
    Slow -> Slow: verify / resolve conflict /\nprepare memory patch
    Slow --> Fast: refined answer\n+ optional memory patch
    Fast --> User: refined answer
end

note over Fast, Slow
Pass structured handoff objects,
not free-form agent chatter.
end note

@enduml
